Description: This MPG has all the cut scenes of all 3 halo games put together as one long movie. i bought the Halo 3 Legendary Edition and i did not like how they made the DVD. in the Halo 3 Legendary Edition they had in game play with the cut scenes, which was a wast of time. also the quality of the Halo 3 Legendary Edition cut scenes where low quality. non of the Halo 3 Legendary Edition was used to make this MPG. i ripped all the cut scenes my self. when i put all the cut scenes together, i was surprize to see how well it came out. its like watching a movie not a game. the story runs smoothly. this MPG also has all halo3 cut scenes (and more) (Halo 3 Legendary Edition does not have that). if you are a HALO fan this is a must for you.

i spent a lot of time on this. i hope you enjoy it ---deathmule

HALO plot: After they crash-land on an artificial ring-world called &quot;Halo&quot;, a navy captain, his surviving marines, and a genetically-and-surgically-enhanced supersoldier called &quot;Master Chief&quot; must find out what the Covenant, the genocidal alien race they are at war with, are looking for on the ring. However, Halo holds more secrets than either side imagined

